  "title": "Dental Assistant 28/01/2026",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>1) Prepare treatment area and trays for dental procedures</p>\n<p>2) Assist dentist during treatment</p>\n<p>3) Manage inventory of dental consumables – Ensure no losses of small instruments</p>\n<p>4) Take and develop x-rays</p>\n<p>5) Observe and Maintain infection control at all times</p>\n<p>6) Record and ensure timely delivery of cases to lab</p>\n<p>7) Helping with infection control by sterilizing and disinfecting instruments - Autoclave Setting up instrument trays, chair, preparing materials, and assisting with dental x- ray procedures</p>\n<p>8) Perform general housekeeping to ensure cleanliness of treatment rooms.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>1) Candidate must possess at least \"N\"/ \"O\" Levels qualification.</p>\n<p>2) 5.5 work day week and must commit to weekday nights and one weekend</p>\n<p>3) Basic computer skills for front desk duties.</p>\n<p>4) Good communication skills.</p>\n<p>5) Able to start work immediately</p>",
