    "uen": "201305746N",
    "description": "<p>Paramount Dental Pte Ltd started as a single treatment unit dental clinic at Block 108, Hougang Avenue 1, with two dental assistants in 2011. We named it Paramount Dental Clinic because we believed every patient's smile is of paramount importance. With this vision in mind, we had slowly expanded our patient's pool, and in 2013, we added another treatment unit in the clinic, with two dentists running both treatment units at the same time.<br>\n<br>\nIn 2013, we started the second clinic at Yishun Ring Road and named it Noble Dental Surgery. The word \" Noble\" came about because we believe in upholding high ethical standards in our treatment philosophy. We think of dentistry as a noble profession that can make a difference in other people's lives.<br>\n<br>\nWith these two principles, we continue to expand our presence to Bedok Central in 2015, Admiralty in 2017, and subsequently Yishun 461 and Ang Mo Kio in 2021.<br>\n<br>\nWe believe in reinvesting our profits to improve patient care and treatment quality. Hence, we have purchased state-of-the-art instruments such as Trios 3D scanner, Cone-Beam CT Machine (3D X-ray machine), CADCAM machines, and more. All these instruments help in improving the precision and quality of dental care. To have better quality control in the products we deliver to our patients, we set up our dental lab in 2018. The dental lab – Trinity Dental Lab is one of the few digital dental labs in Singapore.</p>\n<p><br>\n<strong>Vision:</strong><br>\n<em>\"Your Smile, Our Smiles.\"<br>\nEvery patient's smile is of paramount importance to us. We aim to transform your smile with the highest ethical standard.</em></p>",
